preference.name: Transfer_CO_Notification_Enabled
preference.preference_description: Specifies whether to enable or disable Transfer Checkout notifications for transferor and transferee users. This preference does not disable Transfer Checkout notifications for users added to the notification list. Valid Values: * true: Enables Transfer Checkout notifications for transferor and transferee users. This is the default value. * false: Disables Transfer Checkout notifications for transferor and transferee users.
